# Env files
# .env is committed and holds public Vite vars (VITE_SUPABASE_URL,
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY) — these are designed by Supabase to be public.
# Local-only secrets (SUPABASE_ACCESS_TOKEN, etc.) live in .env.local.
.env.local
.env.*.local

